description:
Why Google for Gen AI? Here's why, and what services and technologies you can develop with Gen AI apps in the Google Cloud.
You can get information to help customers utilize Gen AI in several areas.

Kim Il-ho (Andy)
Currently, I am a Google Cloud Customer Engineering Manager, helping various customers to innovate.
Previously, he was a Cloud Solutions Architect at Amazon since 2013. Recently, we've been delivering a message about Gen AI.
